user.biography:
Just a spunky 2 year old partially blind rescue pup who looks a bit like a Picasso masterpiece!🥴
Adopted from @omkshelter & so loved💙
Brodie stuff!👇😊

node.text: Brodie found one of the last snow piles that hasn’t melted yet, and he had a blast sliding down it and pouncing into the hole he dug! He never ceases to amaze us with the cute things he does 😂❤️ check out the full IGTV video to see the rest of his antics!

node.text: We took Brodie camping in the mountains, it was so much fun!We were playing fetch with a stick and I accidentally threw it in the lake 😩. Even though Brodie was literally surrounded by sticks, he wouldn’t give up on looking for THAT specific one 😂. He continued searching for 5 more minutes until I found another one that was worthy 🤦🏻‍♀️😆 such a silly boy!! ❤️

node.text:
Brodie’s trying out his looks for Halloween! 👻 Which spooktacular outfit is your favorite?! 🧡🖤 #ad

Fall is right around the corner, so be sure to check out all of PetSmart’s costumes at the link in our bio 🎃🧡

We weren't sure how Brodie would feel wearing costumes, but these options from PetSmart are both comfortable for him AND cute! Plus the toys were a big hit. 😏 @petsmart @petsmartcanada #petsmart #halloween
